{"word":"G1833 - ἐξετάζω - exetázō - ex-et-ad'-zo - Ask","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐξετάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">exetázō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ex-et-ad'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Ask</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விசாரி, கேள்"},{"paragraph":"to search out; to examine strictly, inquire"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03C4;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03B6;&#x03C9;</b> <b>etazo&#x0304;</b> (to <i>examine</i>); to <i>test thoroughly</i> (by questions), that is, <i>ascertain</i> or <i>interrogate:</i> - ask, enquire, search.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}